#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:1 of
msgid "Compute the inverse FFT of a signal that has Hermitian symmetry."
msgstr "计算具有 Hermitian 对称性的信号的逆 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:5 of
msgid ""
"Length of the inverse FFT, the number of points along transformation axis"
" in the input to use.  If `n` is smaller than the length of the input, "
"the input is cropped.  If it is larger, the input is padded with zeros. "
"If `n` is not given, the length of the input along the axis specified by "
"`axis` is used."
msgstr ""
"逆 FFT 的长度，即沿变换轴使用的输入点数。如果 `n` 小于输入的长度，则输入"
"会被裁剪。如果 `n` 更大，则输入会用零填充。如果未指定 `n`，则使用沿 `axis"
"` 指定轴的输入长度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:11 of
msgid ""
"Axis over which to compute the inverse FFT. If not given, the last axis "
"is used."
msgstr "计算逆 FFT 所用的轴。如果未指定，则使用最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:14 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `numpy.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `numpy.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:17 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axis"
" indicated by `axis`, or the last one if `axis` is not specified. The "
"length of the transformed axis is ``n//2 + 1``."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，按照 `axis` 指定的轴（或未指定时为最后"
"一个轴）进行变换。变换后轴的长度为 ``n//2 + 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`hfft`, :py:obj:`irfft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:26 of
msgid ""
"`hfft`/`ihfft` are a pair analogous to `rfft`/`irfft`, but for the "
"opposite case: here the signal has Hermitian symmetry in the time domain "
"and is real in the frequency domain. So here it's `hfft` for which you "
"must supply the length of the result if it is to be odd:"
msgstr ""
"`hfft`/`ihfft` 是与 `rfft`/`irfft` 类似的一对函数，但用于相反的情况：这里"
"的信号在时域中具有 Hermitian 对称性，在频域中是实数。因此，如果你希望结果"
"是奇数长度，需要为 `hfft` 提供结果长度："

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:31 of
msgid "even: ``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 2) == a``, within roundoff error,"
msgstr "偶数：``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 2) == a``，在舍入误差范围内，"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:32 of
msgid "odd: ``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 1) == a``, within roundoff error."
msgstr "奇数：``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 1) == a``，在舍入误差范围内。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.ihfft.ihfft:35 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

